f months.\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a set\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1750}, {\"ngram\": \"guards\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1760}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I always had a spare pair of guards in my bag just in case.'\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a spare pair\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"guards\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"my bag\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"case\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A nasty moment for Jesse Moore on the horizontal bar.\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A nasty moment\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"Jesse Moore\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"the horizontal bar\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a4\\u0095Thankfully, the Australian is fine to continue.#BBCOlympics#Olympics#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/vhuCA9V6BJ Dolci was not the only gymnast to suffer a nasty fall in the Olympic final, with Australia's Jesse Moore also hitting the deck after a mistake on the horizontal bar.\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9935060986143299, \"rank\": 0.0055553709074458585, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2092, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9858662374917683, \"rank\": 0.014004179380316024, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://db